rows.label: qst005803_msg0001
rows.name:
After all this digging,
to find nothing...

rows.label: qst005803_msg0002
rows.name:
I wonder if there really was
a kingdom in Liberalitas.

rows.label: qst005803_msg0003
rows.name:
It's a bit small for
a kingdom, isn't it?

rows.label: qst005803_msg0004
rows.name:
Most of it may have sunk into
the Cloud Sea. If so, it would
be impossible to find.

rows.label: qst005803_msg0007
rows.name:
The information in that
ancient book was a lie!

rows.label: qst005803_msg0009
rows.name:
So Tora and friends were dancing
to false information, mo?!

rows.label: qst005803_msg0010
rows.name:
It is truly infuriating, but
that appears to be the case.

rows.label: qst005803_msg0011
rows.name:
To think that I, a king, would
travel to a place without
verifying its authenticity...

rows.label: qst005803_msg0012
rows.name:
However, one cannot move forward
by dwelling on the past.

rows.label: qst005803_msg0013
rows.name:
Let us pull ourselves together
and gather new information!
